snippet.title: Angry Birds Stella: Official Gameplay Trailer!
snippet.description:
Angry Birds Stella is OUT NOW on iOS, Android, NOOK, and BlackBerry 10! Download today and play for free! http://download.stella.angrybirds.com

Angry Birds Stella is the all-new slingshot adventure starring a fearless flock of BFFs with spectacular superpowers! 

Gale – the Bad Princess – has stolen Stella’s precious scrapbook, scattering her priceless memories across magical Golden Island! Join Stella, Dahlia, Poppy, Willow, and Luca as they sling through leafy treetops and sandy beaches using their incredible superpowers! Can you help them reclaim the snapshots and protect their enchanting home from Gale? Oh one other small thing, Gale has a big band of blindly loyal pigs who’ll do whatever she says. We just thought you should know. Good luck!

Find out more about this fearless flock, the action-packed game, and the upcoming Toons series over at http://stella.angrybirds.com
